title: Chronicle of Dalimil - NKP XII E 17
description: Chronicle of Dalimil is a medieval Bohemian chronicle written in verse, detailing the history of Bohemia from its legendary beginnings to the early 14th century.

title: Cosmas of Prague - ÖNB 508
description: Cosmas of Prague was a medieval chronicler and priest known for his work Chronica Boemorum, which provides a detailed account of the history of Bohemia from its legendary origins to the early 12th century.
